# 🏆 Leaderboard App

A real-time leaderboard system where users can be added, selected, and awarded random points.

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: ReactJS + Vite  
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express + MongoDB  
- **Realtime**: Socket.io  

---

## 📦 Features

- 🔁 Realtime leaderboard updates using Socket.io  
- ➕ Add users dynamically  
- 🎲 Claim random points (1–10) per user  
- 📜 Track and display claim history  
- 🥇 Ranking updates automatically based on scores  
- 💾 MongoDB for data persistence  

---

