## 🔧 Getting Started

### 📥 Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ThirumalaNaidu9381/Leader-Board-Front-end.git
cd Leader-Board-Front-end

⚙️ Backend Setup
Navigate to backend:

cd backend

Install dependencies:
npm install

Create .env file:
PORT=5000
MONGO_URL=your_mongodb_connection_string

Start the server:
npm start


🖥️ Frontend Setup

Navigate to frontend:
cd frontend

Install dependencies:
npm install

Start the dev server:
npm run dev
🔗 Deployment
Frontend: Deployed on Vercel

Backend: Hosted on Render

Update .env or API endpoints accordingly in production.

